Buy, make, or reuse a pencil case. In the pencil case put things in like pencils, pens, erasers, sticky notes, etc. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/93/Be-Organized-in-Middle-School-Step-2Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Be-Organized-in-Middle-School-Step-2Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/9/93/Be-Organized-in-Middle-School-Step-2Bullet2.jpg/aid425432-v4-728px-Be-Organized-in-Middle-School-Step-2Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":322,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"510","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
